{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──星期三。第4周的早晨。\n奈奈开始来了三周。她的身心都在稳步变化着。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(她现在每周都来了……我绝对可以称她为常客了。)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(但光靠她一个人,我无法维持店铺运营。我需要想办法吸引更多客人……)"
    },
    {
      "include": "common/weekly_settlement"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "早上好!今天也请多关照。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "早上好,奈奈。看到你这么有精神真好。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "是的!上周的按摩真的很有效……腰痛几乎完全消失了。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "所以……我向朋友们介绍了这家店。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "真的吗?你介绍了?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "是的。我告诉她们感觉很舒服,大家都很感兴趣……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "不过……关于那套衣服我没怎么提……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "(有新客人的可能性……!这是个好机会!)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "那么,今天感觉怎么样?有哪里不舒服吗?"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "嗯……今天……腹部感觉紧绷……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "最近压力太大吃了很多甜食……肚子好像有点胀……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_007"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "腹部紧绷……这样的话,今天试着仰卧进行治疗吧。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "仰卧……是说?和平时姿势不一样啊。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_008"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "是的。仰卧的话我可以好好放松腹部周围的肌肉,调节内脏功能。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "而且,从身体前侧发送波动,可以平衡自律神经系统。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "从前侧……有点害羞……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_009"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "但是我相信老师……就拜托你了。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_010"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "谢谢。你一定会感受到效果的。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "还有……最近身体总感觉发热……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_011"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "晚上很难入睡……而且总是做奇怪的梦……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_012"
    },
    {
      "id": "choice_massage4",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "嗯……这可能是自律神经失调的征兆。",
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "可能是压力",
          "trustDelta": 2,
          "developDelta": 0,
          "next": "stress_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "可能是荷尔蒙失调",
          "trustDelta": 1,
          "developDelta": 1,
          "next": "hormone_path"
        },
        {
          "label": "你的身体可能在渴望什么",
          "trustDelta": 0,
          "developDelta": 2,
          "next": "desire_path"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "stress_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "确实……最近考试很多……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_013"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "压力是万病之源。今天我会好好护理你,让你放松。",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "hormone_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "荷-荷尔蒙平衡……是说……?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_014"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "是的。年轻女性特别容易受影响。对身体变化变得敏感是很自然的。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "这-这样啊……我最近确实感觉身体怪怪的……",
      "next": "change_clothes",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_015"
    },
    {
      "id": "desire_path",
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "诶?我的身体在渴望什么……?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_016"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "你的身体是诚实的。缺少什么的时候,它会发出正确的信号。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "比如……当缺少身体接触或人的温度时……身体会发热。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "不-不会吧……!我不需要那种东西……!",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_017"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "没关系,不用害羞。这是人类自然的欲望。",
      "next": "change_clothes"
    },
    {
      "id": "change_clothes",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "那么,请换衣服吧。今天我会检查腹部区域,所以会格外仔细。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "好-好的……明白了。",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_018"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_lookaway",
      "text": "(已经习惯这套衣服了……但今天还要摸肚子……)",
      "cutInImage": "nana_changing",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_019"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "换好了……",
      "outfit": "micro_bikini",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_020"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "(依然是美妙的身体……而且不知为何,她的皮肤比以前更有光泽了……)"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "很好,准备好了。今天我想尝试一些新技术。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "新技术……是说?",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_021"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "是的。有一种特殊的手法可以调节内脏。可能会有点强烈,不过……"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "我-我没事的……我相信老师……",
      "voiceFile": "story_day4_022"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "(信任……真是个好词。)"
    },
    {
      "id": "massage_start",
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "blush_closemouth",
      "text": "那么,开始吧。"
    }
  ]
}
